snippet.title: Love Verne Prototype Trailer, Ludum Dare 46
snippet.description:
Gameplay for LOVE VERNE, my Ludum Dare 46 entry.

Theme: Keep it Alive.

Play as Fernando, a psychic fern, and care for his nervous pet, Verne! 

"Verne needs to be fed food items, I think, possibly, but I might be overfeeding it. Verne gets more and more stressed out as I feed it. Good thing I took a 2-hour CPR course." 

Thanks for the good feelings!
